{"tid":1594464,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"每晚10點鳩叫係咪少咗人？","createTime":"2019-09-25T14:43:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T16:20:28.000Z","uid":225285,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c2bcdb3dfccae5532bdaf9f017fb77d9ce5489c1","tid":1594464,"uid":225285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T14:43:16.000Z","msg":"每晚10點鳩叫係咪少咗人？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解我嗰區連續兩日都冇咩人，明明之前每一日都有好多把聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86f5e10c2e6c244d55ab65982b7b73e004942a5a","tid":1594464,"uid":167878,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T14:45:50.000Z","msg":"啲人掛住睇tvb<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a45e4ea462a4952b522cb18cd35affd2159cee4","tid":1594464,"uid":225285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86f5e10c2e6c244d55ab65982b7b73e004942a5a","tid":1594464,"uid":167878,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T14:45:50.000Z","msg":"啲人掛住睇tvb<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T14:50:20.000Z","msg":"之前就算我唔帶頭叫，都有好幾把聲叫。但琴日同今日我帶頭叫，回應嘅人5隻手指數得哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f2edef67c65c0a5a5a04790a6b689eb8c93bc7","tid":1594464,"uid":97523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T14:51:19.000Z","msg":"我果邊大圍有手足帶 叫咗半個鍾<br />\n唱咗兩次榮光勁大聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67d9d3625bc685c5332087af3b3b8fa3b32adc8e","tid":1594464,"uid":225285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05f2edef67c65c0a5a5a04790a6b689eb8c93bc7","tid":1594464,"uid":97523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T14:51:19.000Z","msg":"我果邊大圍有手足帶 叫咗半個鍾<br />\n唱咗兩次榮光勁大聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T14:55:10.000Z","msg":"星期二之前，我住嗰邊都叫足半個鐘，就算有藍屍都係照叫。但依兩日真係叫咗十分鐘都唔太多人應<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：啟德"},{"pid":"91c93b14d92ceb789d6cd0b11ef899ae9bcae2b1","tid":1594464,"uid":225285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T14:58:31.000Z","msg":"啟德手足可唔可以每日都堅持叫，唔好比藍屍阻嚇到。<br />\n最多我沙聲都幫你屌藍屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65b842ed186a2d080531fbd7021bf1e7106ace9e","tid":1594464,"uid":70127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:01:48.000Z","msg":"10點鳩叫好似唔及商場唱歌咁LOCAL FEEL"},{"pid":"ad3e36c03eab1ea00bdc3c51d155c2966239aa63","tid":1594464,"uid":276535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:02:38.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10422498136dbfc556464a93f3b119d729f15edf","tid":1594464,"uid":225285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65b842ed186a2d080531fbd7021bf1e7106ace9e","tid":1594464,"uid":70127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:01:48.000Z","msg":"10點鳩叫好似唔及商場唱歌咁LOCAL FEEL"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:05:03.000Z","msg":"不如每晚10點都唱歌為主，口號為輔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />始終有啲人唔方便叫口號"},{"pid":"4d611c3d9fe8ab038786eb83e6f805cfdedf3e75","tid":1594464,"uid":225285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad3e36c03eab1ea00bdc3c51d155c2966239aa63","tid":1594464,"uid":276535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:02:38.000Z","msg":"係<img sr